Package: SummaryWidgets
Title: Crosstalk-enabled summary statistic visualizations
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Jessica", "Lachance", email = "lachje10@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Used with crosstalk, SummaryWidgets display a single summary statistic in a variety of forms. Supported visualizations include an html text span, a gauge and a valuebox.
